{"tid":1867521,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人收到（藍絲？）關於武漢肺炎既電話問卷調查。。。","createTime":"2020-02-07T08:00:58.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-07T08:04:34.000Z","uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"3d913ee7e4abc0c807cc757d82d326c55b18eea6","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:00:58.000Z","msg":"有冇人一樣<br />\n岩岩有個2字頭既電話打黎做問卷調查<br />\n一開始問咩擔問擔心<br />\n但聽落個錄音有d口音有d奇怪<br />\n最尾仲問你支唔支持全面封關<br />\n但比你答之前又講一大輪<br />\n咩全面封關到時候香港社區大爆發<br />\n大陸又全面封關就冇得躲避<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n（翻大陸叫躲避咩？大陸先係源頭啊屌你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係咪政府定咩藍絲機構又想混淆視聽<br />\n話比d老人家定無知婦孺聽封關係唔好既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a08596f1223d80a29727a2904c0c237a00758ace","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"自推幾野先"},{"pid":"dbc7a1d14e44a06b35a258b2638c931e74f8fe54","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:01:42.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"b51fd49ad06dd726ccd76cfcf4df0e7ef761ece0","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:01:55.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"fdb198650b0d351f1a887bab34c671d38d737804","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:02:07.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"87b9fc0e244dd08de089484c69e091b3fc1b7367","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:02:23.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"6e993f06db8692f05d0679bb52a66e29ca5b645f","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:02:35.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"d1c1a3b6cd448b2149b57faa5b735d8ecd94c967","tid":1867521,"uid":316064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-07T08:02:46.000Z","msg":"6"}